{{Infobox Berry |name = Wiki |image = [[File:Wiki.png]] |caption = It is said that this Berry grew lumps to help Pokémon grip it, allowing propagation farther afield. |growtime = 6m 0s |harvest = 15 berries |replant = 30% |points = 45 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 15 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 }} '''Wiki''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 25, but no more than 80 points of dry and less than 5 points of all other flavours. The [[Chesto]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry.
